Platform WebView runtimes (not bundled)
  nativeview links against OS-provided embedding APIs. End-user applications
  must comply with the respective platform terms:

  - macOS / iOS: Apple WebKit (WKWebView) — Apple SDK and App Store terms
  - Windows: Microsoft WebView2 — Microsoft Edge WebView2 license and runtime
    redistribution requirements for packaged apps
  - Linux: WebKitGTK — LGPL; typically satisfied by dynamic linking to system
    libwebkit2gtk and providing source offer where required
  - Android: System WebView / Chromium — Google Play and Android SDK terms

JavaScript bridge bundle
  Built from js/src/ by tools/js_build.py into nativeview.js (MIT/Apache 2.0
  per file headers in the repository).

